[
  {
    "startTime": 15.26,
    "endTime": 18.259999999999998,
    "text": "This cell phone"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.26,
    "endTime": 21.26,
    "text": "started its trajectory"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.26,
    "endTime": 23.26,
    "text": "in an artisanal mine"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.26,
    "endTime": 25.26,
    "text": "in the Eastern Congo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.26,
    "endTime": 27.26,
    "text": "It's mined by armed gangs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.26,
    "endTime": 29.26,
    "text": "using slaves, child slaves,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.26,
    "endTime": 31.26,
    "text": "what the U.N. Security Council"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.26,
    "endTime": 33.260000000000005,
    "text": "calls \"blood minerals,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.26,
    "endTime": 35.26,
    "text": "then traveled into some components"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.26,
    "endTime": 37.26,
    "text": "and ended up in a factory"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.26,
    "endTime": 39.26,
    "text": "in Shinjin in China."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.26,
    "endTime": 42.26,
    "text": "That factory -- over a dozen people have committed suicide"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.26,
    "endTime": 44.26,
    "text": "already this year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.26,
    "endTime": 48.26,
    "text": "One man died after working a 36-hour shift."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.26,
    "endTime": 50.26,
    "text": "We all love chocolate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.26,
    "endTime": 52.26,
    "text": "We buy it for our kids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.26,
    "endTime": 55.26,
    "text": "Eighty percent of the cocoa comes from Cote d'Ivoire and Ghana"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.26,
    "endTime": 58.26,
    "text": "and it's harvested by children."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.26,
    "endTime": 60.26,
    "text": "Cote d'Ivoire, we have a huge problem of child slaves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.26,
    "endTime": 63.26,
    "text": "Children have been trafficked from other conflict zones"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.26,
    "endTime": 66.25999999999999,
    "text": "to come and work on the coffee plantations."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.26,
    "endTime": 68.26,
    "text": "Heparin -- a blood thinner,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.26,
    "endTime": 70.26,
    "text": "a pharmaceutical product --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.26,
    "endTime": 73.26,
    "text": "starts out in artisanal workshops"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.26,
    "endTime": 75.26,
    "text": "like this in China,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.26,
    "endTime": 77.26,
    "text": "because the active ingredient"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.26,
    "endTime": 80.26,
    "text": "comes from pigs' intestines."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.26,
    "endTime": 83.26,
    "text": "Your diamond -- you've all heard, probably seen the movie \"Blood Diamond.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.26,
    "endTime": 85.26,
    "text": "This is a mine in Zimbabwe"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.26,
    "endTime": 87.26,
    "text": "right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.26,
    "endTime": 89.26,
    "text": "Cotton: Uzbekistan is the second biggest"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.26,
    "endTime": 91.26,
    "text": "exporter of cotton on Earth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.26,
    "endTime": 94.26,
    "text": "Every year when it comes to the cotton harvest,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.26,
    "endTime": 96.26,
    "text": "the government shuts down the schools,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.26,
    "endTime": 99.26,
    "text": "puts the kids in buses, buses them to the cotton fields"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.26,
    "endTime": 102.26,
    "text": "to spend three weeks harvesting the cotton."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.26,
    "endTime": 104.26,
    "text": "It's forced child labor"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.26,
    "endTime": 107.26,
    "text": "on an institutional scale."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.26,
    "endTime": 110.26,
    "text": "And all of those products probably end their lives"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.26,
    "endTime": 112.26,
    "text": "in a dump like this one in Manila."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.26,
    "endTime": 115.26,
    "text": "These places, these origins,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.26,
    "endTime": 117.26,
    "text": "represent governance gaps."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.26,
    "endTime": 119.26,
    "text": "That's the politest description"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.26,
    "endTime": 122.26,
    "text": "I have for them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.26,
    "endTime": 124.26,
    "text": "These are the dark pools"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.26,
    "endTime": 127.26,
    "text": "where global supply chains begin --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.26,
    "endTime": 129.26,
    "text": "the global supply chains,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.26,
    "endTime": 132.26,
    "text": "which bring us our favorite brand name products."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.26,
    "endTime": 135.26,
    "text": "Some of these governance gaps"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.26,
    "endTime": 138.26,
    "text": "are run by rogue states."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.26,
    "endTime": 140.26,
    "text": "Some of them are not states anymore at all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.26,
    "endTime": 142.26,
    "text": "They're failed states."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.26,
    "endTime": 144.26,
    "text": "Some of them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.26,
    "endTime": 147.26,
    "text": "are just countries who believe that deregulation or no regulation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.26,
    "endTime": 150.26,
    "text": "is the best way to attract investment,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.26,
    "endTime": 152.26,
    "text": "promote trade."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.26,
    "endTime": 154.26,
    "text": "Either way, they present us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.26,
    "endTime": 158.26,
    "text": "with a huge moral and ethical dilemma."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.26,
    "endTime": 160.26,
    "text": "I know that none of us want to be accessories"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.26,
    "endTime": 163.26,
    "text": "after the fact"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.26,
    "endTime": 165.26,
    "text": "of a human rights abuse"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.26,
    "endTime": 167.26,
    "text": "in a global supply chain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.26,
    "endTime": 169.26,
    "text": "But right now,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.26,
    "endTime": 172.26,
    "text": "most of the companies involved in these supply chains"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.26,
    "endTime": 174.26,
    "text": "don't have any way"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.26,
    "endTime": 176.26,
    "text": "of assuring us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.26,
    "endTime": 178.26,
    "text": "that nobody had to mortgage their future,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.26,
    "endTime": 181.26,
    "text": "nobody had to sacrifice their rights"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.26,
    "endTime": 183.26,
    "text": "to bring us our favorite"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.26,
    "endTime": 186.26,
    "text": "brand name product."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.26,
    "endTime": 188.26,
    "text": "Now, I didn't come here to depress you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.26,
    "endTime": 191.26,
    "text": "about the state of the global supply chain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.26,
    "endTime": 193.26,
    "text": "We need a reality check."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.26,
    "endTime": 196.26,
    "text": "We need to recognize just how serious"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.26,
    "endTime": 199.26,
    "text": "a deficit of rights we have."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.26,
    "endTime": 201.26,
    "text": "This is an independent republic,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.26,
    "endTime": 203.26,
    "text": "probably a failed state."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.26,
    "endTime": 207.26,
    "text": "It's definitely not a democratic state."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.26,
    "endTime": 209.26,
    "text": "And right now,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.26,
    "endTime": 211.26,
    "text": "that independent republic of the supply chain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.26,
    "endTime": 213.26,
    "text": "is not being governed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.26,
    "endTime": 216.26,
    "text": "in a way that would satisfy us,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.26,
    "endTime": 220.26,
    "text": "that we can engage in ethical trade or ethical consumption."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.26,
    "endTime": 222.26,
    "text": "Now, that's not a new story."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.26,
    "endTime": 224.26,
    "text": "You've seen the documentaries"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.26,
    "endTime": 226.26,
    "text": "of sweatshops making garments"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.26,
    "endTime": 229.26,
    "text": "all over the world, even in developed countries."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.26,
    "endTime": 231.26,
    "text": "You want to see the classic sweatshop,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.26,
    "endTime": 233.26,
    "text": "meet me at Madison Square Garden,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.26,
    "endTime": 236.26,
    "text": "I'll take you down the street, and I'll show you a Chinese sweatshop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.26,
    "endTime": 239.26,
    "text": "But take the example of heparin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.26,
    "endTime": 241.26,
    "text": "It's a pharmaceutical product."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.26,
    "endTime": 244.26,
    "text": "You expect that the supply chain that gets it to the hospital,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.26,
    "endTime": 248.26,
    "text": "probably squeaky clean."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.26,
    "endTime": 250.26,
    "text": "The problem is that the active ingredient in there --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.26,
    "endTime": 252.26,
    "text": "as I mentioned earlier --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.26,
    "endTime": 254.26,
    "text": "comes from pigs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.26,
    "endTime": 257.26,
    "text": "The main American manufacturer"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.26,
    "endTime": 259.26,
    "text": "of that active ingredient"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.26,
    "endTime": 262.26,
    "text": "decided a few years ago to relocate to China"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.26,
    "endTime": 265.26,
    "text": "because it's the world's biggest supplier of pigs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.26,
    "endTime": 267.26,
    "text": "And their factory in China --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.26,
    "endTime": 270.26,
    "text": "which probably is pretty clean --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.26,
    "endTime": 272.26,
    "text": "is getting all of the ingredients"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.26,
    "endTime": 274.26,
    "text": "from backyard abattoirs,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.26,
    "endTime": 276.26,
    "text": "where families slaughter pigs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.26,
    "endTime": 279.26,
    "text": "and extract the ingredient."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.26,
    "endTime": 281.26,
    "text": "So a couple of years ago, we had a scandal"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.26,
    "endTime": 283.26,
    "text": "which killed about 80 people around the world,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.26,
    "endTime": 285.26,
    "text": "because of contaminants"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.26,
    "endTime": 288.26,
    "text": "that crept into the heparin supply chain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.26,
    "endTime": 290.26,
    "text": "Worse, some of the suppliers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.26,
    "endTime": 294.26,
    "text": "realized that they could substitute a product"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.26,
    "endTime": 298.26,
    "text": "which mimicked heparin in tests."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.26,
    "endTime": 301.26,
    "text": "This substitute cost nine dollars a pound,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.26,
    "endTime": 304.26,
    "text": "whereas real heparin, the real ingredient,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.26,
    "endTime": 307.26,
    "text": "cost 900 dollars a pound."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.26,
    "endTime": 309.26,
    "text": "A no-brainer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.26,
    "endTime": 312.26,
    "text": "The problem was that it killed more people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.26,
    "endTime": 314.26,
    "text": "And so you're asking yourself,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.26,
    "endTime": 316.26,
    "text": "\"How come the U.S. Food and Drug Administration"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.26,
    "endTime": 318.26,
    "text": "allowed this to happen?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.26,
    "endTime": 320.26,
    "text": "How did the Chinese State Agency for Food and Drugs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.26,
    "endTime": 322.26,
    "text": "allow this to happen?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.26,
    "endTime": 325.26,
    "text": "And the answer is quite simple:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.26,
    "endTime": 327.26,
    "text": "the Chinese define these facilities"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.26,
    "endTime": 330.26,
    "text": "as chemical facilities, not pharmaceutical facilities,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.26,
    "endTime": 332.26,
    "text": "so they don't audit them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.26,
    "endTime": 334.26,
    "text": "And the USFDA"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.26,
    "endTime": 336.26,
    "text": "has a jurisdictional problem."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.26,
    "endTime": 338.26,
    "text": "This is offshore."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.26,
    "endTime": 340.26,
    "text": "They actually do conduct a few investigations overseas --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.26,
    "endTime": 343.26,
    "text": "about a dozen a year -- maybe 20 in a good year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.26,
    "endTime": 345.26,
    "text": "There are 500"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.26,
    "endTime": 347.26,
    "text": "of these facilities"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.26,
    "endTime": 350.26,
    "text": "producing active ingredients in China alone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.26,
    "endTime": 353.26,
    "text": "In fact, about 80 percent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.26,
    "endTime": 355.26,
    "text": "of the active ingredients in medicines now"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.26,
    "endTime": 357.26,
    "text": "come from offshore,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.26,
    "endTime": 359.26,
    "text": "particularly China and India,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 359.26,
    "endTime": 362.26,
    "text": "and we don't have a governance system."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.26,
    "endTime": 364.26,
    "text": "We don't have a regulatory system"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.26,
    "endTime": 366.26,
    "text": "able to ensure"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.26,
    "endTime": 370.26,
    "text": "that that production is safe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370.26,
    "endTime": 372.26,
    "text": "We don't have a system to ensure"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.26,
    "endTime": 374.26,
    "text": "that human rights, basic dignity,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.26,
    "endTime": 377.26,
    "text": "are ensured."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.26,
    "endTime": 380.26,
    "text": "So at a national level --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.26,
    "endTime": 382.26,
    "text": "and we work in about 60 different countries --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 382.26,
    "endTime": 384.26,
    "text": "at a national level"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 384.26,
    "endTime": 386.26,
    "text": "we've got a serious breakdown in the ability of governments"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 386.26,
    "endTime": 389.26,
    "text": "to regulate production"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.26,
    "endTime": 392.26,
    "text": "on their own soil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.26,
    "endTime": 394.26,
    "text": "And the real problem with the global supply chain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 394.26,
    "endTime": 396.26,
    "text": "is that it's supranational."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 396.26,
    "endTime": 398.26,
    "text": "So governments who are failing,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.26,
    "endTime": 400.26,
    "text": "who are dropping the ball"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 400.26,
    "endTime": 402.26,
    "text": "at a national level,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.26,
    "endTime": 404.26,
    "text": "have even less ability to get their arms around the problem"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.26,
    "endTime": 407.26,
    "text": "at an international level."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 407.26,
    "endTime": 409.26,
    "text": "And you can just look at the headlines."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.26,
    "endTime": 412.26,
    "text": "Take Copenhagen last year --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 412.26,
    "endTime": 414.26,
    "text": "complete failure of governments"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 414.26,
    "endTime": 416.26,
    "text": "to do the right thing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 416.26,
    "endTime": 419.26,
    "text": "in the face of an international challenge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.26,
    "endTime": 422.26,
    "text": "Take the G20 meeting a couple of weeks ago --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 422.26,
    "endTime": 427.26,
    "text": "stepped back from its commitments of just a few months ago."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 427.26,
    "endTime": 429.26,
    "text": "You can take any one"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 429.26,
    "endTime": 432.26,
    "text": "of the major global challenges we've discussed this week"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 432.26,
    "endTime": 435.26,
    "text": "and ask yourself, where is the leadership from governments"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.26,
    "endTime": 438.26,
    "text": "to step up and come up with solutions,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 438.26,
    "endTime": 440.26,
    "text": "responses,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.26,
    "endTime": 443.26,
    "text": "to those international problems?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 443.26,
    "endTime": 447.26,
    "text": "And the simple answer is they can't. They're national."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 447.26,
    "endTime": 449.26,
    "text": "Their voters are local."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 449.26,
    "endTime": 451.26,
    "text": "They have parochial interests."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.26,
    "endTime": 453.26,
    "text": "They can't subordinate those interests"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 453.26,
    "endTime": 456.26,
    "text": "to the greater global public good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456.26,
    "endTime": 458.26,
    "text": "So, if we're going to ensure the delivery"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458.26,
    "endTime": 460.26,
    "text": "of the key public goods"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 460.26,
    "endTime": 462.26,
    "text": "at an international level --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 462.26,
    "endTime": 465.26,
    "text": "in this case, in the global supply chain --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 465.26,
    "endTime": 468.26,
    "text": "we have to come up with a different mechanism."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 468.26,
    "endTime": 472.26,
    "text": "We need a different machine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.26,
    "endTime": 476.26,
    "text": "Fortunately, we have some examples."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 476.26,
    "endTime": 478.26,
    "text": "In the 1990s,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.26,
    "endTime": 480.26,
    "text": "there were a whole series of scandals"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 480.26,
    "endTime": 482.26,
    "text": "concerning the production of brand name goods in the U.S. --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 482.26,
    "endTime": 484.26,
    "text": "child labor, forced labor,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 484.26,
    "endTime": 487.26,
    "text": "serious health and safety abuses."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 487.26,
    "endTime": 489.26,
    "text": "And eventually President Clinton, in 1996,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489.26,
    "endTime": 492.26,
    "text": "convened a meeting at the White House,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 492.26,
    "endTime": 495.26,
    "text": "invited industry, human rights NGOs,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 495.26,
    "endTime": 497.26,
    "text": "trade unions, the Department of Labor,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 497.26,
    "endTime": 499.26,
    "text": "got them all in a room"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 499.26,
    "endTime": 501.26,
    "text": "and said, \"Look,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501.26,
    "endTime": 503.26,
    "text": "I don't want globalization to be a race to the bottom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 503.26,
    "endTime": 505.26,
    "text": "I don't know how to prevent that,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505.26,
    "endTime": 507.26,
    "text": "but I'm at least going to use my good offices"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.26,
    "endTime": 509.26,
    "text": "to get you folks together"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 509.26,
    "endTime": 512.26,
    "text": "to come up with a response.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 512.26,
    "endTime": 514.26,
    "text": "So they formed a White House task force,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 514.26,
    "endTime": 517.26,
    "text": "and they spent about three years arguing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 517.26,
    "endTime": 520.26,
    "text": "about who takes how much responsibility"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 520.26,
    "endTime": 523.26,
    "text": "in the global supply chain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 523.26,
    "endTime": 526.26,
    "text": "Companies didn't feel it was their responsibility."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 526.26,
    "endTime": 528.26,
    "text": "They don't own those facilities."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 528.26,
    "endTime": 530.26,
    "text": "They don't employ those workers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 530.26,
    "endTime": 533.26,
    "text": "They're not legally liable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 533.26,
    "endTime": 535.26,
    "text": "Everybody else at the table"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.26,
    "endTime": 537.26,
    "text": "said, \"Folks, that doesn't cut it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 537.26,
    "endTime": 540.26,
    "text": "You have a custodial duty, a duty of care,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 540.26,
    "endTime": 542.26,
    "text": "to make sure that that product"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 542.26,
    "endTime": 545.26,
    "text": "gets from wherever to the store"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 545.26,
    "endTime": 548.26,
    "text": "in a way that allows us to consume it,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 548.26,
    "endTime": 551.26,
    "text": "without fear of our safety,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 551.26,
    "endTime": 555.26,
    "text": "or without having to sacrifice our conscience"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 555.26,
    "endTime": 557.26,
    "text": "to consume that product.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 557.26,
    "endTime": 560.26,
    "text": "So they agreed, \"Okay, what we'll do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.26,
    "endTime": 562.26,
    "text": "is we agree on a common set of standards,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 562.26,
    "endTime": 564.26,
    "text": "code of conduct."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 564.26,
    "endTime": 566.26,
    "text": "We'll apply that throughout"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 566.26,
    "endTime": 568.26,
    "text": "our global supply chain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 568.26,
    "endTime": 570.26,
    "text": "regardless of ownership or control."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 570.26,
    "endTime": 573.26,
    "text": "We'll make it part of the contract.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 573.26,
    "endTime": 576.26,
    "text": "And that was a stroke of absolute genius,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 576.26,
    "endTime": 578.26,
    "text": "because what they did"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 578.26,
    "endTime": 581.26,
    "text": "was they harnessed the power of the contract,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 581.26,
    "endTime": 583.26,
    "text": "private power,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 583.26,
    "endTime": 585.26,
    "text": "to deliver public goods."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 585.26,
    "endTime": 587.26,
    "text": "And let's face it,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.26,
    "endTime": 589.26,
    "text": "the contract from a major multinational brand"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 589.26,
    "endTime": 592.26,
    "text": "to a supplier in India or China"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 592.26,
    "endTime": 594.26,
    "text": "has much more persuasive value"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 594.26,
    "endTime": 596.26,
    "text": "than the local labor law,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 596.26,
    "endTime": 598.26,
    "text": "the local environmental regulations,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 598.26,
    "endTime": 601.26,
    "text": "the local human rights standards."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 601.26,
    "endTime": 604.26,
    "text": "Those factories will probably never see an inspector."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 604.26,
    "endTime": 607.26,
    "text": "If the inspector did come along,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 607.26,
    "endTime": 609.26,
    "text": "it would be amazing if they were able"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.26,
    "endTime": 613.26,
    "text": "to resist the bribe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 613.26,
    "endTime": 615.26,
    "text": "Even if they did their jobs,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 615.26,
    "endTime": 619.26,
    "text": "and they cited those facilities for their violations,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 619.26,
    "endTime": 621.26,
    "text": "the fine would be derisory."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 621.26,
    "endTime": 623.26,
    "text": "But you lose that contract"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 623.26,
    "endTime": 625.26,
    "text": "for a major brand name,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 625.26,
    "endTime": 627.26,
    "text": "that's the difference"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 627.26,
    "endTime": 630.26,
    "text": "between staying in business or going bankrupt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.26,
    "endTime": 632.26,
    "text": "That makes a difference."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 632.26,
    "endTime": 634.26,
    "text": "So what we've been able to do"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.26,
    "endTime": 636.26,
    "text": "is we've been able to harness"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 636.26,
    "endTime": 638.26,
    "text": "the power and the influence"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 638.26,
    "endTime": 641.26,
    "text": "of the only truly transnational institution"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 641.26,
    "endTime": 643.26,
    "text": "in the global supply chain,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 643.26,
    "endTime": 646.26,
    "text": "that of the multinational company,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.26,
    "endTime": 648.26,
    "text": "and get them to do the right thing,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 648.26,
    "endTime": 651.26,
    "text": "get them to use that power for good,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 651.26,
    "endTime": 655.26,
    "text": "to deliver the key public goods."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 655.26,
    "endTime": 657.26,
    "text": "Now of course, this doesn't come naturally"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 657.26,
    "endTime": 659.26,
    "text": "to multinational companies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 659.26,
    "endTime": 662.26,
    "text": "They weren't set up to do this. They're set up to make money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 662.26,
    "endTime": 665.26,
    "text": "But they are extremely efficient organizations."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 665.26,
    "endTime": 667.26,
    "text": "They have resources,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 667.26,
    "endTime": 670.26,
    "text": "and if we can add the will, the commitment,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 670.26,
    "endTime": 675.26,
    "text": "they know how to deliver that product."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.26,
    "endTime": 678.26,
    "text": "Now, getting there is not easy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 678.26,
    "endTime": 681.26,
    "text": "Those supply chains I put up on the screen earlier,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 681.26,
    "endTime": 683.26,
    "text": "they're not there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 683.26,
    "endTime": 685.26,
    "text": "You need a safe space."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.26,
    "endTime": 688.26,
    "text": "You need a place where people can come together,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 688.26,
    "endTime": 690.26,
    "text": "sit down without fear of judgment,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 690.26,
    "endTime": 692.26,
    "text": "without recrimination,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 692.26,
    "endTime": 694.26,
    "text": "to actually face the problem,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 694.26,
    "endTime": 697.26,
    "text": "agree on the problem and come up with solutions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 697.26,
    "endTime": 700.26,
    "text": "We can do it. The technical solutions are there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 700.26,
    "endTime": 703.26,
    "text": "The problem is the lack of trust, the lack of confidence,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.26,
    "endTime": 705.26,
    "text": "the lack of partnership"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 705.26,
    "endTime": 707.26,
    "text": "between NGOs, campaign groups,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 707.26,
    "endTime": 710.26,
    "text": "civil society organizations"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 710.26,
    "endTime": 713.26,
    "text": "and multinational companies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 713.26,
    "endTime": 716.26,
    "text": "If we can put those two together in a safe space,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 716.26,
    "endTime": 718.26,
    "text": "get them to work together,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 718.26,
    "endTime": 721.26,
    "text": "we can deliver public goods right now,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 721.26,
    "endTime": 724.26,
    "text": "or in extremely short supply."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 724.26,
    "endTime": 726.26,
    "text": "This is a radical proposition,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 726.26,
    "endTime": 728.26,
    "text": "and it's crazy to think"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 728.26,
    "endTime": 731.26,
    "text": "that if you're a 15-year-old Bangladeshi girl"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 731.26,
    "endTime": 734.26,
    "text": "leaving your rural village"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 734.26,
    "endTime": 737.26,
    "text": "to go and work in a factory in Dhaka --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 737.26,
    "endTime": 742.26,
    "text": "22, 23, 24 dollars a month --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 742.26,
    "endTime": 745.26,
    "text": "your best chance of enjoying rights at work"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 745.26,
    "endTime": 747.26,
    "text": "is if that factory is producing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 747.26,
    "endTime": 749.26,
    "text": "for a brand name company"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 749.26,
    "endTime": 751.26,
    "text": "which has got a code of conduct"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 751.26,
    "endTime": 755.26,
    "text": "and made that code of conduct part of the contract."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 755.26,
    "endTime": 757.26,
    "text": "It's crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 757.26,
    "endTime": 759.26,
    "text": "Multinationals are protecting human rights."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 759.26,
    "endTime": 761.26,
    "text": "I know there's going to be disbelief."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 761.26,
    "endTime": 763.26,
    "text": "You'll say, \"How can we trust them?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 763.26,
    "endTime": 765.26,
    "text": "Well, we don't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 765.26,
    "endTime": 767.26,
    "text": "It's the old arms control phrase:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 767.26,
    "endTime": 769.26,
    "text": "\"Trust, but verify.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 769.26,
    "endTime": 771.26,
    "text": "So we audit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 771.26,
    "endTime": 774.26,
    "text": "We take their supply chain, we take all the factory names,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 774.26,
    "endTime": 776.26,
    "text": "we do a random sample,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 776.26,
    "endTime": 779.26,
    "text": "we send inspectors on an unannounced basis"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 779.26,
    "endTime": 781.26,
    "text": "to inspect those facilities,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 781.26,
    "endTime": 783.26,
    "text": "and then we publish the results."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 783.26,
    "endTime": 787.26,
    "text": "Transparency is absolutely critical to this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 787.26,
    "endTime": 790.26,
    "text": "You can call yourself responsible,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 790.26,
    "endTime": 793.26,
    "text": "but responsibility without accountability"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 793.26,
    "endTime": 795.26,
    "text": "often doesn't work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 795.26,
    "endTime": 798.26,
    "text": "So what we're doing is, we're not only enlisting the multinationals,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 798.26,
    "endTime": 801.26,
    "text": "we're giving them the tools to deliver this public good --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 801.26,
    "endTime": 803.26,
    "text": "respect for human rights --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 803.26,
    "endTime": 805.26,
    "text": "and we're checking."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 805.26,
    "endTime": 807.26,
    "text": "You don't need to believe me. You shouldn't believe me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 807.26,
    "endTime": 810.26,
    "text": "Go to the website. Look at the audit results."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 810.26,
    "endTime": 812.26,
    "text": "Ask yourself, is this company behaving"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 812.26,
    "endTime": 815.26,
    "text": "in a socially responsible way?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 815.26,
    "endTime": 817.26,
    "text": "Can I buy that product"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 817.26,
    "endTime": 820.26,
    "text": "without compromising my ethics?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 820.26,
    "endTime": 825.26,
    "text": "That's the way the system works."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 825.26,
    "endTime": 827.26,
    "text": "I hate the idea"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 827.26,
    "endTime": 830.26,
    "text": "that governments are not protecting human rights around the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 830.26,
    "endTime": 832.26,
    "text": "I hate the idea"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 832.26,
    "endTime": 834.26,
    "text": "that governments have dropped this ball"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 834.26,
    "endTime": 837.26,
    "text": "and I can't get used to the idea"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 837.26,
    "endTime": 840.26,
    "text": "that somehow we can't get them to do their jobs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 840.26,
    "endTime": 842.26,
    "text": "I've been at this for 30 years,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 842.26,
    "endTime": 844.26,
    "text": "and in that time I've seen"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 844.26,
    "endTime": 847.26,
    "text": "the ability, the commitment, the will of government"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 847.26,
    "endTime": 849.26,
    "text": "to do this decline,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 849.26,
    "endTime": 852.26,
    "text": "and I don't see them making a comeback right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 852.26,
    "endTime": 854.26,
    "text": "So we started out thinking"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 854.26,
    "endTime": 856.26,
    "text": "this was a stopgap measure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 856.26,
    "endTime": 859.26,
    "text": "We're now thinking that, in fact,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 859.26,
    "endTime": 861.26,
    "text": "this is probably the start"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 861.26,
    "endTime": 864.26,
    "text": "of a new way of regulating and addressing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 864.26,
    "endTime": 866.26,
    "text": "international challenges."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 866.26,
    "endTime": 869.26,
    "text": "Call it network governance. Call it what you will."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 869.26,
    "endTime": 872.26,
    "text": "The private actors,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 872.26,
    "endTime": 874.26,
    "text": "companies and NGOs,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 874.26,
    "endTime": 876.26,
    "text": "are going to have to get together"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 876.26,
    "endTime": 878.26,
    "text": "to face the major challenges we are going to face."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 878.26,
    "endTime": 880.26,
    "text": "Just look at pandemics --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 880.26,
    "endTime": 883.26,
    "text": "swine flu, bird flu, H1N1."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 883.26,
    "endTime": 885.26,
    "text": "Look at the health systems in so many countries."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 885.26,
    "endTime": 887.26,
    "text": "Do they have the resources"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 887.26,
    "endTime": 890.26,
    "text": "to face up to a serious pandemic?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 890.26,
    "endTime": 892.26,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 892.26,
    "endTime": 895.26,
    "text": "Could the private sector and NGOs"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 895.26,
    "endTime": 897.26,
    "text": "get together and marshal a response?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 897.26,
    "endTime": 899.26,
    "text": "Absolutely."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 899.26,
    "endTime": 901.26,
    "text": "What they lack is that safe space"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 901.26,
    "endTime": 903.26,
    "text": "to come together, agree"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 903.26,
    "endTime": 905.26,
    "text": "and move to action."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 905.26,
    "endTime": 909.26,
    "text": "That's what we're trying to provide."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 909.26,
    "endTime": 911.26,
    "text": "I know as well"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 911.26,
    "endTime": 913.26,
    "text": "that this often seems"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 913.26,
    "endTime": 915.26,
    "text": "like an overwhelming level of responsibility"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 915.26,
    "endTime": 917.26,
    "text": "for people to assume."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 917.26,
    "endTime": 919.26,
    "text": "\"You want me to deliver human rights"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 919.26,
    "endTime": 921.26,
    "text": "throughout my global supply chain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 921.26,
    "endTime": 924.26,
    "text": "There are thousands of suppliers in there.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 924.26,
    "endTime": 927.26,
    "text": "It seems too daunting, too dangerous,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 927.26,
    "endTime": 929.26,
    "text": "for any company to take on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 929.26,
    "endTime": 931.26,
    "text": "But there are companies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 931.26,
    "endTime": 934.26,
    "text": "We have 4,000 companies who are members."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 934.26,
    "endTime": 936.26,
    "text": "Some of them are very, very large companies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 936.26,
    "endTime": 938.26,
    "text": "The sporting goods industry, in particular,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 938.26,
    "endTime": 941.26,
    "text": "stepped up to the plate and have done it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 941.26,
    "endTime": 945.26,
    "text": "The example, the role model, is there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 945.26,
    "endTime": 947.26,
    "text": "And whenever we discuss"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 947.26,
    "endTime": 949.26,
    "text": "one of these problems that we have to address --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 949.26,
    "endTime": 952.26,
    "text": "child labor in cottonseed farms in India --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 952.26,
    "endTime": 956.26,
    "text": "this year we will monitor 50,000 cottonseed farms in India."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 956.26,
    "endTime": 958.26,
    "text": "It seems overwhelming."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 958.26,
    "endTime": 961.26,
    "text": "The numbers just make you want to zone out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 961.26,
    "endTime": 964.26,
    "text": "But we break it down to some basic realities."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 964.26,
    "endTime": 966.26,
    "text": "And human rights"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 966.26,
    "endTime": 969.26,
    "text": "comes down to a very simple proposition:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 969.26,
    "endTime": 972.26,
    "text": "can I give this person their dignity back?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 972.26,
    "endTime": 974.26,
    "text": "Poor people,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 974.26,
    "endTime": 976.26,
    "text": "people whose human rights have been violated --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 976.26,
    "endTime": 978.26,
    "text": "the crux of that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 978.26,
    "endTime": 980.26,
    "text": "is the loss of dignity,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 980.26,
    "endTime": 982.26,
    "text": "the lack of dignity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 982.26,
    "endTime": 985.26,
    "text": "It starts with just giving people back their dignity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 985.26,
    "endTime": 988.26,
    "text": "I was sitting in a slum outside Gurgaon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 988.26,
    "endTime": 990.26,
    "text": "just next to Delhi,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 990.26,
    "endTime": 993.26,
    "text": "one of the flashiest, brightest new cities"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 993.26,
    "endTime": 996.26,
    "text": "popping up in India right now,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 996.26,
    "endTime": 998.26,
    "text": "and I was talking to workers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 998.26,
    "endTime": 1000.26,
    "text": "who worked in garment sweatshops down the road,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1000.26,
    "endTime": 1004.26,
    "text": "and I asked them what message they would like me to take to the brands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1004.26,
    "endTime": 1007.26,
    "text": "They didn't say money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1007.26,
    "endTime": 1010.26,
    "text": "They said, \"The people who employ us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1010.26,
    "endTime": 1013.26,
    "text": "treat us like we are less than human,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1013.26,
    "endTime": 1015.26,
    "text": "like we don't exist."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1015.26,
    "endTime": 1019.26,
    "text": "Please ask them to treat us like human beings.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1019.26,
    "endTime": 1021.26,
    "text": "That's my simple understanding of human rights."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1021.26,
    "endTime": 1024.26,
    "text": "That's my simple proposition to you,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1024.26,
    "endTime": 1027.26,
    "text": "my simple plea to every decision-maker"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1027.26,
    "endTime": 1029.26,
    "text": "in this room, everybody out there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1029.26,
    "endTime": 1031.26,
    "text": "We can all make a decision"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1031.26,
    "endTime": 1033.26,
    "text": "to come together"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1033.26,
    "endTime": 1036.26,
    "text": "and pick up the balls and run with the balls"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1036.26,
    "endTime": 1038.26,
    "text": "that governments have dropped."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1038.26,
    "endTime": 1040.26,
    "text": "If we don't do it,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1040.26,
    "endTime": 1042.26,
    "text": "we're abandoning hope,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1042.26,
    "endTime": 1045.26,
    "text": "we're abandoning our essential humanity,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1045.26,
    "endTime": 1047.26,
    "text": "and I know that's not a place we want to be,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1047.26,
    "endTime": 1049.26,
    "text": "and we don't have to be there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1049.26,
    "endTime": 1051.26,
    "text": "So I appeal to you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1051.26,
    "endTime": 1053.26,
    "text": "Join us, come into that safe space,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1053.26,
    "endTime": 1055.26,
    "text": "and let's start to make this happen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1055.26,
    "endTime": 1057.26,
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 1057.26,
    "endTime": 1067.26,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  }
]